'''''Kanneer Pookkal''''' is a [[1981 in film|1981]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by [[Rajasekhar (director)|Rajasekhar]] for Jayavel Productions. The film stars [[Vijayan (actor)|Vijayan]], [[Sripriya]] and [[Roopa (actress)|Roopa]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Kanneer Pookkal LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/417/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-04-25|}}</ref>

